  <!-- Hero / Welcome Section -->
  <section class="section hero-section">
    <h1>Empowering Rural Communities, Transforming Lives</h1>
    <p>
      Welcome to <strong>Wonta Rural Development Association</strong>, where we believe every rural community deserves access to education, healthcare, and sustainable livelihoods. Since our founding, we have been dedicated to creating programs that make a tangible difference in the lives of people living in underserved areas.
    </p>
    <p>
      Our initiatives focus on education, healthcare, women & youth empowerment, and sustainable agriculture. Every project is guided by the needs of the community, ensuring lasting, meaningful change.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- Image Gallery Section -->
  <section class="section">
    <h2>Our Work in Action</h2>
    <div class="gallery index-gallery">
      <img src="/images/nebir.jpg" alt="Community Work">
      <img src="/images/tota.jpg" alt="Health Program">
      <img src="/images/project1.jpg" alt="Women Empowerment">
      <img src="/images/project2.jpg" alt="Agriculture Project">
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About Section -->
  <section class="section">
    <h2>About Us</h2>
    <p>
      <strong>Wonta Rural Development Association</strong> is committed to improving the quality of life in rural areas. We work closely with communities to implement initiatives in education, health, agriculture, and women empowerment, creating opportunities for growth and self-reliance.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- Programs Section -->
  <section class="section">
    <h2>Our Programs</h2>
    <ul class="programs-list">
      <li><strong>Education & Literacy:</strong> Providing children and adults with learning materials, schools, and skill-building programs.</li>
      <li><strong>Healthcare & Sanitation:</strong> Organizing health camps, awareness drives, and access to clean water.</li>
      <li><strong>Women & Youth Empowerment:</strong> Vocational training, microfinance, and leadership programs to uplift communities.</li>
      <li><strong>Sustainable Agriculture:</strong> Helping farmers adopt eco-friendly practices to increase productivity and income.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <!-- Call-to-Action Section -->
  <section class="section cta-section">
    <h2>Get Involved</h2>
    <p>Volunteer, donate, or partner with us to help rural communities grow stronger and more self-reliant. Your support can transform lives.</p>
    <div class="cta-buttons">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-donate">Donate Now</a>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-volunteer">Become a Volunteer</a>
    </div>
  </section>

